9️⃣ SAFETY RULES
Settings must:
    • Never mutate completed run data
    • Never delete session records directly
    • Never allow downgrade to break historical structure
    • Require confirmation for archive
    • Require Admin privilege for mutation
    • Log every configuration change

🔟 HOT–WARM–COLD CONTROL FLOW
Settings triggers:
Active Year → Lock
Lock → Archive
Archive → BigQuery export
BigQuery export → Clear HOT partition
Initialize new HOT partition
Settings never directly queries sessions.
All archival done via batch jobs.

1️⃣1️⃣ UX PRINCIPLES
Settings must:
    • Separate operational from destructive actions
    • Clearly label irreversible operations
    • Group high-risk under “Advanced”
    • Provide preview before archive
    • Provide export backup option
No analytics content mixed here.

